Female/immature.description: Black-headed Grosbeaks overlap with Rose-breasted Grosbeaks only in the Great Plains. Female/immature Black-headed Grosbeaks usually have buffy-orange underparts with less streaking than Rose-breasted. They also tend to have a buffier eyebrow.

Female/immature (Eastern).description: Female/immature Purple Finches are considerably smaller than Rose-breasted Grosbeaks with a smaller bill.
